title: Cafe Nostalgica
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Canadian, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Cafe owned and operated by the Grad Students' Association at the university. The brunch menu includes vegan pancakes and a vegan breakfast sandwich. The regular menu has around 6 vegan items plus a daily vegan special and vegan soup of the day. Uses tofu, tempeh, veggie burger, vegan cheese. Hosts live house band Tuesdays, jazz night Wednesdays, open mic Thursdays.
